packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker (Limited Pride Edition), left
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: Limited Pride edition of the PIXLwear P1 sneaker featuring a full rainbow. #LOVEISLOVE. Only 32 pairs will ever be minted! The P1 model rocks the iconic PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces but not on the sides, and of course the PIXL P1 stamp on the sole. The insoles feature a clever P1 design wrapping onto the back of the shoe. This is the left shoe in rainbow colours. Designer: Pixls.eth. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear (a PIXL brand) - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
